cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with face reenactment using deep learning techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel learning-based framework for face reenactment. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques to transfer facial movements and expressions from one person to another. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with video input and generating reenacted faces. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating photo-realistic faces using a boundary-based transfer method.
